summary: If there would be a crossover between Game of Thrones and Star Wars, with whom would they bond together?
body:
If there would be a crossover between Game of Thrones and Star Wars, with whom would they bond together?

Tarkin: Tywin Lannister. They both plan to kill everyone in very sadistic ways

Thrawn: Tyrion. I mean c'mon. Two outsiders with a love for books. I bet Thrawn convinces Tyrion to look at any art the way he does

Eli: probably Podrick because they are both cinnamon rolls but with a attitude

Pryce: Arya. They teach one another to kill people and to manipulate people. And they totally have a “to kill list” they really are going after

Yularen: eh, maybe with Varys. Both are at least logic thinking persons who have a goal to achieve

Hux:…..Sansa. Gingers rule!

Phasma: Brienne there is no one else. But I bet they both argue about the way they kill and if it’s really neccessary to kill. Also they both want to punch a certain gold handed knight (Phasma punched him at least one time)

Mitaka: Gendry. Both are absolutely cinnamon rolls but Gendry teaches Mitaka to stand up for himself and maybe about how to smith

summary:
Kylo : I've got an army and powerful guns and ships. I will track down the Resistance and destroy them all.
Hux : Supreme...
body:
Kylo : I’ve got an army and powerful guns and ships. I will track down the Resistance and destroy them all.

Hux : Supreme Leader-

Kylo : Quiet. What kind of Supreme Leader am I if I can’t do what I want and destroy everyone I want and when I want-

Hux : Adequate?

Officer :

Kylo : Why are you staring at me like that for?

Officer : *stuttering* I’m sorry, sir. I don’t-

Kylo : Should I destroy you, too? Fucking easy.

Kylo : I’ll wave my hand and you’re dead.

title: Jedi na vida real: Michelle C Smith mostra seus golpes
body:
Jedi na vida real: Michelle C Smith mostra seus golpes

Michelle C Smith é uma dublê, empresária, palestrante e educadora que mostra alguns de seus vídeos de artes marciais e como é ser uma Jedi na vida real na Internet.

Neste em específico ela coloca algumas manobras com um sabre de luz, que mostra como é ser um guerreiro da saga Star Wars.

A moça gira o sabre de luz e o corpo com facilidade, realizando pulos que deixaria qualquer Darth Maul no…
